## Notes

- TanStack removed the built-in CLI MCP server; use this project's local MCP wrapper or CLI commands instead.
- For React projects, include `--framework react` when searching Start, Router, Query, or Form docs.
- DevTools is alpha; CLI docs include add-on scaffolding and the MCP migration guide.
